{{recipe}} | [[Cookbook:Cuisine of Spain|Cuisine of Spain]] | [[Cookbook:Egg|Egg Recipes]] | [[Cookbook:Healthy, Traditional Recipes|Healthy, Traditional Recipes]] {{recipesummary|Spanish recipes|2 to 3|15 to 20 minutes|1}}
The '''''tortilla canaria''''' (Spanish for Canary Islands omelet) originated in Spain's Canary Islands, an island chain to the southwest of Spain and off the western coast of Africa.
Canary Islands cuisine fuses Spanish cooking traditions with those of Africa, Latin America and the Guanche people who were original inhabitants of the Canaries. Also, it utilizes local fish, fruits and vegetables. <ref>[http://www.red2000.com/spain/canarias/gastro.html Info on the cuisine of the Canary Islands]</ref>
The traditional recipe, shown below, calls for an omelet filled with sauted tomatoes, onions and garlic, seasoned with tarragon, parsley, salt and sometimes [[cookbook:basil|basil]].<ref>José María Campos and Joan Masats, ''La Cocina Española: Entrantes y Primeros Platos.'' Printer Industria Trafica S.A., page 92.</ref> <ref>[http://www.cocinaisabel.com/tag/huevos/page/2/ Recipe for the ''tortilla canaria'']</ref> Variations can include [[cookbook:rice|rice]] and a wide variety of vegetables.
==Ingredients== *2 Tablespoons [[cookbook:olive oil|olive oil]] *150 grams [[cookbook:onions|yellow onions]], diced *2 cloves [[cookbook:garlic|garlic]], chopped *1 teaspoon [[cookbook:parsley|parsley]] *1 teaspoon [[cookbook:tarragon|tarragon]] *300 grams [[cookbook:tomato|tomatoes]], diced *[[cookbook:salt|salt to taste]] *6 [[cookbook:eggs|eggs]], scrambled
==Procedure== #[[cookbook:saute|Sauté]] the onions and the chopped garlic in olive oil with the parsley and tarragon until the garlic is slightly brown. #Add the tomatoes and salt. Saute until the tomatoes are tender. Remove from heat. #Make two open omelets from the scrambled eggs. #Place the cooked vegetables into the center of each omelette and fold them over. #Serve hot. {{wikipedia|Tortilla canaria}}
==References== {{reflist}}
[[Category:Tomato recipes]] [[Category:Omelette recipes]] [[Category:Pan fried recipes]] [[Category:Breakfast recipes]] [[Category:Recipes_with_metric_units|{{PAGENAME}}]]

